detail.name: Meta-Cooler
detail.effect:
[Permanent] You can include as many copies of this card in your deck as you like.
[When KO'd] Play up to 1 <Meta-Cooler> with a cost of 3 from your hand.

detail.name: メタルクウラ
detail.effect:
[永続]このカードはデッキに何枚でも入れることができる。
[KO時]自分の手札のコスト3の「メタルクウラ」1枚までを登場させる。

faq.question: Does this card's [Permanent] skill also allow you to include 5 or more copies of this card in your deck?
faq.answer: Yes, as long as the total number of cards in your deck is 60 or less, you can include as many copies of this card in your deck as you like.

faq.question: When this card's [When KO'd] skill activates, can you play up to 1 [Meta-Cooler] card with a cost of 3 from your hand in Rest Mode?
faq.answer: No, you can't. Unless specified otherwise, you must play it in Active Mode.

faq.question: このカードの【永続】は、デッキに5枚以上入れることもできるということですか？
faq.answer: はい、デッキの上限60枚以下であれば任意の枚数入れることができます。

faq.question: このカードの【KO時】を発動した時、手札のコスト3の「メタルクウラ」1枚までをレストで登場させることはできますか？
faq.answer: いいえ、できません。特に指定がない場合、アクティブで登場させます。
